company.taskMan

Class ProjectView

  • java.lang.Object
    • company.taskMan.ProjectView

  • public class ProjectView
extends java.lang.Object
    A projectView is a wrapper for projects. The projectView only has limited access to the project and is thus safe to send out to the UI. The UI will hence also only have limited access to the underlying projects and cannot do anything unauthorized.
    Author:
    Tim Van den Broecke, Joran Van de Woestijne, Vincent Van Gestel and Eli Vangrieken
